Jaipur, the Pink City, is a mesmerizing blend of rich heritage and vibrant culture. From the stunning architecture of the Hawa Mahal to the majestic Amer Fort, every corner tells a story. Join me as I wander through the streets, capturing the essence of Jaipur’s beauty and charm!
